1. *Zabava* je trajala do ranog jutra. (The party lasted until early morning.)
2. On je organizovao *zabavu* za svoju decu. (He organized a party for his children.)
3. Ona je došla kasno na *zabavu*. (She arrived late to the party.)
4. Njegovi roditelji nisu dozvolili da ide na *zabavu*. (His parents did not allow him to go to the party.)
5. *Zabave* se održavaju u obližnjem parku. (Parties are held in the nearby park.) 
6. Često se održavaju *zabave* za decu. (Parties for children are often held.)
7. *Zabavljali* smo se do kasno u noć. (We had fun until late at night.)
8. Oni su se *zabavljali* na svojoj proslavi. (They had fun at their celebration.)